caption: The image is an invitation for a Chinese New Year party on January 22, 2022. The event will take place on Sunday from 5:00 PM to 10:00 PM. The location is the Jamie Chastain House, located at 123 Anywhere St., Any City. The invitation features a festive red background and includes a cartoon illustration of a man and a girl holding a gift. The image conveys a sense of excitement and celebration for the upcoming Chinese New Year party.
original_title: Red And Gold Illustration Chinese New Year Party Instagram Story
